Schnitt and his wife are suing Clem, claiming he made 'false, highly 
offensive and defamatory' statements about them.

Incidents include when Clem called former Assistant State Attorney Michelle Schnitt, who often appeared on her husband's show, a 'whore,' reported the Tampa Bay Times.

The spate began when Clem accused Schnitt of accepting favours and gifts from businesses in exchange for plugs on the air.

