He then accused Mrs Schnitt of conspiring with State Attorney Mark Ober to bring animal cruelty charges against him after in 20001 after he presided over the slaughter and barbecue of a wild boar on-air.

Although Clem was later acquitted of animal cruelty, he vowed revenge against the Schnitts for being prosecuted.

On Wednesday, Clem said the accusations and name-calling were all just an act and that he only the attacked the Schnitt's alter ego, MJ Kelli.

